{"word":"στρέφω","slug":"στρέφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>στρέφω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘redirect a position’, <b>turn<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a>, of a body part, the cheek <b><a href='B:470 5:39'>Mt 5:39</a>.</b> Abs., of God turning away, suggesting dissociation <b><a href='B:510 7:42'>Ac 7:42</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on being in position to face an entity<b> <a href='B:470 7:6'>Mt 7:6</a>; <a href='B:470 9:22'>9:22</a>; <a href='B:470 16:23'>16:23</a>; <a href='B:490 7:9'>Lk 7:9</a>, <a href='B:490 7:44'>44</a>; <a href='B:490 9:55'>9:55</a>; <a href='B:490 10:22'>10:22</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>, 23; <a href='B:490 14:25'>14:25</a>; <a href='B:490 22:61'>22:61</a>; <a href='B:490 23:28'>23:28</a>; <a href='B:500 1:38'>J 1:38</a>; <a href='B:500 20:16'>20:16</a>.</b> Cp. <b><a href='B:510 7:39'>Ac 7:39</a>; <a href='B:510 13:46'>13:46</a>.</b> <el>ἐστράφη <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:εἰς\">εἰς</a> τὰ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀπίσω\">ὀπίσω</a></el> she turned around <b><a href='B:500 20:14'>J 20:14</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘bring back to a location’, <b>return <a href='B:470 27:3'>Mt 27:3</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘make totally different’, <b>transform, turn <a href='B:730 11:6'>Rv 11:6</a>.</b> In imagery, of inward change <b><a href='B:470 18:3'>Mt 18:3</a>; <a href='B:500 12:40'>J 12:40</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:στρεβλόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:στρέψον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}